output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Presence: - Yes, contains CMF: 11240017, indicating it's electoral propaganda
2. Candidate Reference: - Mentions Marcel Ciolacu, who is a presidential candidate - Also discusses parliamentary candidates, but in a broader context
3. Addresses Wide Population: - Paid advertisement reaching 45,000-50,000 impressions - Published on both Facebook and Instagram - Clearly intended for mass communication
4. Electoral Objective: - Uses campaign slogans "#CaleaSigurăPentruRomânia" - Explicitly mentions "campania electorală" - Promotes PSD candidates and their projects - References "alegerile din următoarele săptămâni"
5. Journalism vs Propaganda: - This is clearly campaign material, not journalism - Contains personal endorsements and campaign messaging
6. Personal Opinion: - While containing personal elements, this is a structured campaign message
The post violates Article 55 t) as it continues electoral propaganda for the presidential elections (by mentioning Marcel Ciolacu and his "proiecte de țară") after the conclusion of the presidential campaign period.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains official CMF number - Paid distribution with significant reach - Uses campaign slogans - Explicitly promotes candidates and their projects - Mentions both parliamentary and presidential campaigns
conclusion.message-for-police: PSD Maramureș, prin reprezentantul Gabriel Valer Zetea, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale pentru candidatul prezidențial Marcel Ciolacu după încheierea perioadei de campanie. Postarea cu ID-ul 1120036146358587 promovează explicit "proiectele de țară propuse de Marcel Ciolacu" într-o postare plătită, cu impact semnificativ (45,000-50,000 impresii), difuzată după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Postarea include elementele specifice propagandei electorale: CMF 11240017, sloganuri de campanie, și promovare directă a candidatului prezidențial într-o perioadă interzisă de lege.
